{"type":"route","meta":{"status":200,"headers":{"content-type":"text/markdown","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/llms.mdx/layout,_N_T_/llms.mdx/docs/layout,_N_T_/llms.mdx/docs/[[...slug]]/layout,_N_T_/llms.mdx/docs/[[...slug]]/route,_N_T_/llms.mdx/docs/content.md"}},"body":"# Welcome to NxCut (/docs)\n\n\n\nWelcome to **NxCut** — your all-in-one salon management system. Whether you're booking an appointment, collecting payment, managing your team, or checking how your business is doing, everything you need is right here.\n\nThis guide walks you through every part of NxCut in plain, simple language. No technical experience needed.\n\n***\n\nWhat can NxCut do for you? [#what-can-nxcut-do-for-you]\n\n<Cards>\n  <Card title=\"Dashboard\" href=\"/docs/dashboard\" description=\"See how your business is doing at a glance — revenue, appointments, and top performers.\" />\n\n  <Card title=\"Calendar & Bookings\" href=\"/docs/calendar\" description=\"Book, reschedule, and manage appointments for your whole team in one view.\" />\n\n  <Card title=\"Checkout\" href=\"/docs/checkout\" description=\"Collect payment, apply discounts, add tips, and split bills — all in a few clicks.\" />\n\n  <Card title=\"Sales Hub\" href=\"/docs/sales\" description=\"View your full sales history — payments, memberships, vouchers, tips, and more.\" />\n\n  <Card title=\"Catalog & Inventory\" href=\"/docs/catalog\" description=\"Set up your services, products, membership packages, and gift vouchers.\" />\n\n  <Card title=\"Clients\" href=\"/docs/clients\" description=\"Keep a full record of every client — their visits, memberships, and voucher balances.\" />\n\n  <Card title=\"Team Management\" href=\"/docs/team\" description=\"Add staff, set their working hours, and control what they can access.\" />\n\n  <Card title=\"Commission\" href=\"/docs/commission\" description=\"Automatically calculate how much each team member earns and generate salary slips.\" />\n\n  <Card title=\"Reporting\" href=\"/docs/reporting\" description=\"Dig into your numbers — sales trends, payment breakdowns, tips, and more.\" />\n\n  <Card title=\"Settings\" href=\"/docs/settings\" description=\"Set up your locations, business hours, payment options, and access rules.\" />\n\n  <Card title=\"Website & Booking Page\" href=\"/docs/website\" description=\"Manage your public booking page and let clients book appointments online.\" />\n</Cards>\n\n***\n\nFinding your way around [#finding-your-way-around]\n\nWhen you log in, you'll see a menu on the left side of the screen. Each item takes you to a different part of NxCut.\n\n| Section                        | What it's for                     | Who can see it |\n| ------------------------------ | --------------------------------- | -------------- |\n| [Dashboard](/docs/dashboard)   | Business overview and key numbers | Admins only    |\n| [Calendar](/docs/calendar)     | Appointments and bookings         | All staff      |\n| [Sales](/docs/sales)           | Sales history and transactions    | All staff      |\n| [Clients](/docs/clients)       | Client directory and profiles     | All staff      |\n| [Catalog](/docs/catalog)       | Services, products, and packages  | All staff      |\n| [Team](/docs/team)             | Staff profiles and schedules      | All staff      |\n| [Commission](/docs/commission) | Earnings and salary slips         | Admins only    |\n| [Reports](/docs/reporting)     | Financial reports and analytics   | Admins only    |\n| [Settings](/docs/settings)     | Business configuration            | Admins only    |\n\n<Callout type=\"info\">\n  **Admin vs. Staff** — Admin users can access everything. Regular staff only see what they need for their daily work: Calendar, Sales, Clients, Catalog, and Team.\n</Callout>\n"}